WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 28=

01:48.850 --> 01:49.820
Xing?

01:50.740 --> 01:51.770
I was wondering

01:51.770 --> 01:54.690
why the magpies
wouldn't stop chattering.

01:54.690 --> 01:56.850
So, Miss Cai is back
with the Young Master.

01:59.020 --> 02:00.130
We...

02:00.770 --> 02:02.620
I understand.

02:02.980 --> 02:03.820
Understand what?

02:04.490 --> 02:06.900
You stormed the execution ground
for the Young Master.

02:06.900 --> 02:08.380
The whole sect already knows.

02:08.380 --> 02:09.940
Throughout the sect,

02:09.940 --> 02:11.410
everyone admires you.

02:11.850 --> 02:14.130
They all say you're bold and decisive,

02:14.130 --> 02:16.010
born to be one of us.

02:16.540 --> 02:18.060
We've all agreed

02:18.060 --> 02:19.690
you are our future lady.

02:19.690 --> 02:20.940
What lady?

02:20.940 --> 02:22.010
That's nonsense.

02:22.260 --> 02:23.500
I'm not making it up.

02:23.940 --> 02:25.500
Elder Yan agrees too.

02:27.820 --> 02:28.730
Oh, right.

02:28.730 --> 02:29.780
After Nie Zhe returned,

02:30.100 --> 02:31.500
Elder Yan scolded him

02:31.690 --> 02:33.060
in front of everyone,

02:33.540 --> 02:35.730
saying he nearly ruined
the sect's foundation.

02:36.130 --> 02:37.780
He couldn't kill Elder Yan,

02:37.780 --> 02:40.340
so he locked him back
in the Jiuzhou Archive.

02:40.340 --> 02:42.410
That does sound like Elder Yan.

02:42.410 --> 02:44.010
Young Master, you may not know.

02:44.010 --> 02:44.850
Nie...

02:47.980 --> 02:48.820
Xing,

02:49.610 --> 02:52.380
let the Young Master
and Miss Cai wash up first.

02:52.780 --> 02:53.969
We'll talk about anything else

02:53.980 --> 02:54.820
in the village.

02:56.730 --> 02:57.570
Right.

02:58.060 --> 02:59.410
Mr. and Mrs. Mu,

02:59.410 --> 03:00.290
come with us.

03:00.370 --> 03:01.220
Let's go.

03:01.220 --> 03:02.610
Aren't you going to explain?

03:03.060 --> 03:03.900
Explain what?

03:04.610 --> 03:05.450
We...

03:07.130 --> 03:07.970
Forget it.

03:28.660 --> 03:30.730
You Guanyue is shameless.

03:31.260 --> 03:33.500
Once he heard of the capture,
he defected to Nie Zhe.

03:33.850 --> 03:34.996
I cut ties with him long ago.

03:36.060 --> 03:37.220
Don't worry, Young Master.

03:37.690 --> 03:39.540
Everyone's heart is with you.

03:40.130 --> 03:42.660
Though you haven't led the sect
for long,

03:42.660 --> 03:43.690
you've truly done

03:43.690 --> 03:44.730
a lot for us.

03:45.660 --> 03:47.220
We've all been hoping for your return.

03:48.060 --> 03:49.500
He's done a lot?

03:50.100 --> 03:50.980
Yes.

03:51.290 --> 03:52.850
The Young Master exempted our taxes

03:52.850 --> 03:55.110
and allowed us to travel freely
in the Hanhai Mountains.

03:55.610 --> 03:57.450
Otherwise, how could Grandfather
and I go out?

04:01.220 --> 04:02.060
Young Master,

04:02.380 --> 04:03.980
when will you reclaim Bliss Palace?

04:07.010 --> 04:07.850
Wait a little longer.

04:09.290 --> 04:10.170
Listen to me rambling.

04:10.660 --> 04:12.130
The Young Master is still injured.

04:13.010 --> 04:15.290
Uncle Xue should be back
with the herbs soon.

04:15.290 --> 04:16.170
Village Chief.

04:16.780 --> 04:17.780
Speak of the devil.

04:18.250 --> 04:20.610
I brought back every herb I could find.

04:20.610 --> 04:21.582
- Give it to me.
- Xing.

04:21.593 --> 04:23.113
- I'll go dry them.
- Sure.

04:25.140 --> 04:26.010
Uncle Xue.

04:26.030 --> 04:27.170
Miss Cai.

04:27.170 --> 04:28.020
Long time no see.

04:28.290 --> 04:29.220
Yes.

04:29.220 --> 04:30.100
Well.

04:30.100 --> 04:31.020
This is...?

04:35.490 --> 04:36.330
Zhengyang?

04:39.780 --> 04:40.620
What relation

04:41.250 --> 04:42.370
are you to Zhengyang?

04:43.140 --> 04:44.370
If I'm not mistaken,

04:45.020 --> 04:46.540
the person you mentioned

04:47.050 --> 04:48.250
should be his uncle,

04:48.780 --> 04:49.620
Mu Zhengyang.

04:59.700 --> 05:01.370
She was the best girl in the world.

05:02.100 --> 05:03.370
Her heart is pure

05:04.370 --> 05:05.780
like a clear sky.

05:06.610 --> 05:08.340
Which family was she from?

05:08.340 --> 05:09.220
What was her name?

05:10.220 --> 05:11.250
Her name is

05:11.580 --> 05:12.420
Pingshu.

05:15.930 --> 05:16.770
She gave me

05:17.580 --> 05:18.900
this wrist guard.

05:23.290 --> 05:25.930
Did Mu Zhengyang truly love that girl?

05:25.930 --> 05:26.770
Of course.

05:27.340 --> 05:29.930
Zhengyang would've given her
his very heart.

05:30.370 --> 05:31.483
When he came back that time,

05:31.740 --> 05:32.610
he said

05:32.610 --> 05:34.780
Pingshu had agreed to marry him.

05:35.050 --> 05:36.370
Once he finished his great cause,

05:36.370 --> 05:38.020
he'd choose an auspicious day to wed.

05:38.900 --> 05:39.740
He even said

05:40.100 --> 05:42.100
he'd bring her to meet me.

05:43.730 --> 05:44.570
But

05:45.340 --> 05:46.490
after that,

05:47.850 --> 05:49.340
I never saw him again.

05:55.340 --> 05:56.700
He's gone.

05:59.540 --> 06:00.380
Actually,

06:01.580 --> 06:02.980
I had already guessed.

06:03.580 --> 06:04.490
I just

06:04.490 --> 06:05.370
had no confirmation

06:06.340 --> 06:07.660
and didn't want to face it.

06:10.580 --> 06:11.420
By the way,

06:12.780 --> 06:14.900
Pingshu...

06:17.410 --> 06:18.700
She's gone too.

06:19.980 --> 06:20.820
Life

06:21.780 --> 06:22.730
is too unpredictable.

06:23.540 --> 06:26.050
If Zhengyang hadn't gone
to do that great cause

06:26.410 --> 06:28.700
and had chosen to marry Pingshu instead,

06:31.220 --> 06:32.780
how wonderful that would've been.

06:48.020 --> 06:49.553
The great cause Mu Zhengyang mentioned

06:50.780 --> 06:52.170
must have been to reclaim

06:52.170 --> 06:54.290
the Chief position
taken by Nie Hengcheng.

07:02.370 --> 07:03.580
I don't understand.

07:04.810 --> 07:06.730
If Mu Zhengyang truly loved my aunt

07:07.540 --> 07:09.220
and had a feud with Nie Hengcheng,

07:11.340 --> 07:13.610
why would he kill her close friends

07:14.140 --> 07:15.810
and leave her to fight Nie alone?

07:20.900 --> 07:22.930
I planned to find out
who the man in black is.

07:24.170 --> 07:25.340
After killing Nie Zhe,

07:26.730 --> 07:28.220
I'd seal the Youming Path,

07:29.290 --> 07:30.370
restrain the sect members,

07:30.980 --> 07:32.930
and prevent further conflict
with the Six Sects.

07:33.660 --> 07:34.500
That way,

07:37.700 --> 07:39.410
I could marry you openly and honorably.

07:59.050 --> 08:00.050
But now,

08:01.170 --> 08:02.416
I don't want to wait any longer.

08:04.220 --> 08:05.410
I'm afraid of losing you.

08:10.050 --> 08:10.890
Zhao,

08:12.660 --> 08:13.540
let's get married.

08:50.700 --> 08:51.540
Aunt.

09:02.060 --> 09:02.900
Zhao.

09:18.010 --> 09:19.650
The skin-painted demon.

10:11.010 --> 10:12.420
Those people from the Six Sects

10:12.420 --> 10:13.260
are nothing to fear.

10:13.910 --> 10:14.820
That's good.

10:14.820 --> 10:15.660
Shisan?

10:17.340 --> 10:18.340
Miss Cai.

10:18.650 --> 10:20.550
Wasn't it said Nie Zhe seized power,

10:20.940 --> 10:23.370
and you were injured
and fled with Uncle Cheng?

10:23.770 --> 10:24.650
I am unharmed.

10:25.700 --> 10:26.940
Uncle Cheng heard the news

10:26.940 --> 10:28.540
and sent me to protect the Young Master

10:28.551 --> 10:29.210
and you.

10:31.340 --> 10:32.239
Good that you're fine.

10:34.610 --> 10:35.503
At the market outside,

10:35.514 --> 10:37.180
there were a few spies
from the Six Sects.

10:37.180 --> 10:38.820
Did you run into them on your way here?

10:38.820 --> 10:39.730
They should be gone.

10:42.820 --> 10:43.700
Where is Mu Qingyan?

11:07.100 --> 11:08.250
Thanks to your snow lotus,

11:09.126 --> 11:11.179
the Cold Spirit Powder poison
in my body has eased.

11:11.420 --> 11:12.260
In that case,

11:12.980 --> 11:14.250
I can return with peace of mind.

11:15.220 --> 11:16.060
Return?

11:19.490 --> 11:20.330
Zhao,

11:21.490 --> 11:23.056
I know you're worried
about your master

11:23.530 --> 11:24.370
and your parents

11:24.683 --> 11:25.949
and want to go back to see them.

11:26.340 --> 11:27.180
How about this?

11:27.700 --> 11:29.133
Once the Six Sects stop pursuing us,

11:29.650 --> 11:30.610
I'll go back with you.

11:34.100 --> 11:35.370
It's been days.

11:36.577 --> 11:37.923
They should've calmed down by now.

11:41.060 --> 11:42.100
Just as you expected.

11:42.730 --> 11:43.820
Just as I expected?

11:48.980 --> 11:49.890
What do you mean?

11:50.530 --> 11:52.490
Before entering the Hanhai Mountains,

11:52.490 --> 11:55.010
I noticed
the Six Sects' pursuers dwindling.

11:56.250 --> 11:57.130
Only today

11:57.700 --> 11:58.610
did I confirm

11:59.890 --> 12:00.770
they withdrew.

12:02.300 --> 12:04.770
What method could make

12:05.370 --> 12:08.220
the Six Sects abandon the hunt?

12:10.610 --> 12:12.250
Did you seize their families?

12:14.730 --> 12:15.610
Whom did you capture?

12:16.940 --> 12:17.980
Zhou Yuqi?

12:35.850 --> 12:36.730
Xinrou,

12:36.730 --> 12:37.570
rest assured.

12:37.940 --> 12:39.060
I've informed my mother.

12:39.490 --> 12:40.610
I'll formally marry you soon.

12:41.010 --> 12:42.060
Those rumors

12:42.300 --> 12:43.420
will vanish

12:43.980 --> 12:45.650
once we wed.

12:55.580 --> 12:56.420
What's going on?

12:59.250 --> 13:00.090
Mr. Zhou,

13:01.060 --> 13:02.100
come with me.

13:04.650 --> 13:06.060
Guangtian Sect and Siqi Sect

13:06.650 --> 13:08.100
weren't spared either, right?

13:08.860 --> 13:13.180
(Song Xiuzhi, Guangtian Sect)

13:13.180 --> 13:14.020
Who?

13:21.010 --> 13:22.060
Who are you?

13:28.980 --> 13:30.770
Your father schemes day and night

13:30.770 --> 13:31.850
for your sake.

13:31.850 --> 13:33.530
Why wear that long face all day?

13:36.890 --> 13:37.730
Mrs. Yang,

13:37.940 --> 13:38.850
Miss Yang,

13:38.850 --> 13:39.820
come with us.

13:47.490 --> 13:49.010
Qingque Sect is heavily guarded

13:50.130 --> 13:50.970
and hard to strike.

13:51.370 --> 13:53.820
Taichu Temple is in chaos;
you have nothing to fear.

13:54.340 --> 13:55.490
As for Luoying Valley,

13:59.130 --> 14:00.580
whether you seize them or not

14:01.730 --> 14:02.940
makes little difference.

14:04.850 --> 14:06.340
Why would I do this?

14:08.130 --> 14:10.220
This is your chain scheme,

14:11.340 --> 14:13.300
and seizing the Six Sects' families

14:14.130 --> 14:16.250
is the final link.

14:22.610 --> 14:24.060
A chain scheme?

14:25.890 --> 14:27.490
The opening move of your grand game

14:28.730 --> 14:30.490
was to lure out Nie Zhe's remnants

14:31.099 --> 14:32.345
and wipe them out in one sweep.

14:33.180 --> 14:34.213
Defeating Nie Zhe is easy,

14:35.060 --> 14:37.650
but uprooting the Nie clan's
decades-long foundation

14:38.130 --> 14:39.220
is far harder.

14:39.580 --> 14:41.770
Moreover, many
have feigned allegiance to you.

14:42.530 --> 14:43.820
You can't launch a massacre.

14:44.580 --> 14:45.420
So,

14:46.100 --> 14:47.100
your second move

14:47.530 --> 14:49.010
was to use yourself as bait,

14:49.340 --> 14:50.610
enter the game personally,

14:51.770 --> 14:53.580
come to Qingque Sect to see me,

14:53.580 --> 14:54.820
and be captured on purpose.

14:58.890 --> 15:01.490
That way, those hidden Nie loyalists

15:01.490 --> 15:04.010
and the opportunistic turncoats

15:04.010 --> 15:04.940
would expose themselves.

15:06.130 --> 15:07.403
Nie Zhe is suspicious by nature,

15:08.770 --> 15:09.610
and

15:09.820 --> 15:11.220
the man in black behind him

15:11.820 --> 15:13.490
knows the Six Sects inside out.

15:14.300 --> 15:15.890
Without something real,

15:16.180 --> 15:17.490
they wouldn't fall for it.

15:21.130 --> 15:23.010
Once news of your capture spread,

15:23.730 --> 15:25.010
they'd take the bait.

15:25.530 --> 15:26.730
As for the final step,

15:27.580 --> 15:29.466
you can use the hostages
in your hand to escape

15:30.010 --> 15:31.370
and purge the sect.

15:31.820 --> 15:33.700
Truly meticulous.

15:34.220 --> 15:35.890
Every move is linked.

15:42.850 --> 15:44.340
If that were true,

15:45.890 --> 15:48.420
wouldn't I be some mighty monster?

15:49.250 --> 15:51.250
Lord Qi often says
I'm a skin-painted demon.

15:52.220 --> 15:53.490
It seems

15:53.940 --> 15:55.250
you took those words to heart.

15:57.850 --> 15:59.300
But have you thought about this?

15:59.530 --> 16:01.420
If I wanted to seize
the Six Sects' families,

16:02.010 --> 16:03.239
it'd take at least half a month

16:03.250 --> 16:04.530
just to gather them.

16:05.490 --> 16:07.103
There wouldn't be time for me to escape.

16:07.610 --> 16:08.770
I'd still end up

16:09.060 --> 16:10.580
with my martial arts crippled.

16:22.610 --> 16:25.770
That was the most crucial move
in your game.

16:31.700 --> 16:32.580
You were gambling.

16:35.530 --> 16:36.730
You were gambling

16:37.180 --> 16:38.940
on whether I'd defy my elders

16:39.250 --> 16:40.890
and risk everything to save you.

16:44.100 --> 16:44.940
Mu Qingyan,

16:48.370 --> 16:49.250
you won.

16:50.580 --> 16:51.420
Master,

16:51.730 --> 16:52.730
please let him go.

16:55.850 --> 16:57.130
From beginning to end,

16:58.220 --> 17:00.530
everyone was within your calculations.

17:01.770 --> 17:02.700
Even I

17:03.890 --> 17:05.620
was just

17:07.490 --> 17:09.180
a convenient chess piece,

17:09.980 --> 17:10.820
right?

17:21.420 --> 17:22.380
These herbs

17:22.730 --> 17:24.140
will help clear

17:24.620 --> 17:25.810
the remaining poison in you.

17:28.860 --> 17:29.700
From now on,

17:31.380 --> 17:32.530
take care of yourself.

17:50.900 --> 17:52.770
I never saw you as a chess piece.

17:57.660 --> 17:58.500
Zhao,

18:00.810 --> 18:02.330
I know you can't bear to leave me.

18:02.330 --> 18:07.040
♪If we never met♪

18:07.050 --> 18:08.620
I can't bear to leave you either.

18:10.770 --> 18:12.570
We promised to rely on each other.

18:13.220 --> 18:14.250
You promised me.

18:14.860 --> 18:15.700
Let go.

18:18.700 --> 18:19.540
Mu Qingyan.

18:21.740 --> 18:24.070
♪We already brushed past♪

18:24.250 --> 18:25.330
Have some respect.

18:33.940 --> 18:36.330
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

18:37.010 --> 18:37.850
Cai Zhao!

18:41.060 --> 18:42.810
♪Holding you and me♪

18:42.810 --> 18:47.140
♪Life spreads without boundary♪

18:47.250 --> 18:48.530
The Six Sects' families

18:49.530 --> 18:50.730
are in my hands.

18:50.730 --> 18:53.100
♪Before death♪

18:54.660 --> 18:55.900
If you dare leave,

18:58.420 --> 18:59.620
I'll kill them.

19:25.730 --> 19:29.790
♪We don't have to meet again♪

19:30.380 --> 19:31.730
If you want to save them,

19:32.090 --> 19:33.050
come with me.

19:41.140 --> 19:41.980
Master,

19:42.330 --> 19:44.116
all those sent to pursue Zhao
have withdrawn.

19:44.290 --> 19:45.900
But Mu Qingyan hasn't released them.

19:46.140 --> 19:47.420
They're in his hands.

19:49.180 --> 19:50.490
We can only wait.

19:50.490 --> 19:51.900
I said long ago

19:51.900 --> 19:53.530
we shouldn't have captured Mu Qingyan.

19:53.770 --> 19:55.220
He's a hot potato.

19:55.810 --> 19:56.650
Now, look.

19:56.810 --> 19:58.330
We lost Zhao

19:58.700 --> 20:00.050
and several young heirs.

20:01.250 --> 20:03.290
Mu Qingyan's foundation isn't stable.

20:03.559 --> 20:05.752
I'm certain he wouldn't wage war
against the Six Sects

20:06.180 --> 20:08.050
or harm those families.

20:08.290 --> 20:09.700
As for some physical suffering,

20:10.380 --> 20:11.420
that's unavoidable.

20:12.090 --> 20:14.620
I never imagined
Mu Qingyan's schemes ran so deep.

20:15.330 --> 20:16.170
If Zhao

20:16.570 --> 20:18.220
was also within his schemes...

20:18.220 --> 20:19.060
Rest assured.

20:20.420 --> 20:21.530
Though Mu Qingyan

20:22.770 --> 20:24.220
is skilled at disguising himself,

20:24.570 --> 20:26.380
Zhao is exceptionally clever.

20:26.786 --> 20:28.140
Her heart is as clear as a mirror.

20:28.140 --> 20:29.010
She'll figure out

20:29.620 --> 20:30.700
many things.

20:31.090 --> 20:32.660
Once she understands,

20:33.490 --> 20:34.940
she will return on her own.

21:24.010 --> 21:25.220
Mu Qingyan has been captured!

21:43.900 --> 21:45.090
It seems you

21:45.570 --> 21:46.676
couldn't bear for me to die.

21:46.900 --> 21:47.740
Mu Qingyan,

21:48.290 --> 21:49.130
you lied to me again.

22:01.980 --> 22:03.420
Welcome, Chief.

22:13.490 --> 22:14.330
Mu Qingyan,

22:15.290 --> 22:17.660
last time you hid for over a year.

22:18.140 --> 22:20.090
Why so impatient this time?

22:20.530 --> 22:21.700
I got a little bored waiting.

22:22.530 --> 22:23.700
Is everyone here?

22:23.700 --> 22:24.540
I suppose

22:25.140 --> 22:27.050
no one would want to miss

22:27.700 --> 22:29.530
such great merit as killing a Mu.

22:29.530 --> 22:30.370
Mu Qingyan,

22:31.380 --> 22:33.106
you're infatuated
with Cai Pingshu's niece.

22:33.530 --> 22:35.050
For personal feelings,

22:35.050 --> 22:36.690
you've repeatedly put the sect
in danger.

22:37.127 --> 22:38.500
You're unworthy of being the Chief.

22:38.660 --> 22:40.180
If you surrender now,

22:40.900 --> 22:42.090
Chief Nie is merciful.

22:42.330 --> 22:43.860
Perhaps he'll spare your life.

22:48.700 --> 22:49.540
Zhao,

22:50.380 --> 22:51.290
did you hear that?

22:51.860 --> 22:53.660
The whole world knows

22:53.660 --> 22:54.940
I'm hopelessly in love with you.

22:55.770 --> 22:56.610
Shut up.

22:57.220 --> 22:59.033
Don't tell me
this was part of your plan too.

22:59.730 --> 23:00.570
Zhao,

23:01.810 --> 23:03.770
don't you want to see us

23:05.250 --> 23:06.420
avenge Uncle Chang?

23:20.090 --> 23:20.930
Father.

23:25.180 --> 23:27.010
You Guanyue. Shangguan.

23:29.010 --> 23:31.980
So, Mr. Mu has learned

23:31.980 --> 23:33.660
to use women and children as hostages.

23:33.660 --> 23:35.050
Chief, you misunderstand.

23:35.050 --> 23:37.290
I just discovered something shocking

23:37.290 --> 23:39.250
and rushed here

23:39.250 --> 23:41.440
to report it.

23:41.450 --> 23:42.330
Chief,

23:42.330 --> 23:43.330
no need to waste words.

23:43.330 --> 23:44.530
Everything is in position.

23:44.860 --> 23:46.180
Take your family and break out.

23:47.700 --> 23:48.730
Mr. Yu,

23:48.730 --> 23:49.730
no rush.

23:50.530 --> 23:51.370
After all,

23:51.620 --> 23:52.730
blades have no eyes.

23:53.290 --> 23:54.490
If Mrs. Nie or your and her son

23:54.900 --> 23:56.940
were injured...

23:56.940 --> 23:57.780
You Guanyue,

23:58.420 --> 23:59.530
stop your nonsense.

24:00.050 --> 24:02.660
I've long heard that Mr. Yu and Mrs. Nie

24:02.660 --> 24:04.770
were childhood sweethearts.

24:05.330 --> 24:06.330
Coincidentally,

24:06.860 --> 24:08.660
a few days ago, Elder Yan got drunk

24:08.940 --> 24:10.620
and mentioned the Yu clan.

24:10.620 --> 24:12.380
Their butterfly bone is distinctive.

24:12.380 --> 24:14.730
There's a green mark along the bone,

24:14.730 --> 24:15.730
and it's hereditary.

24:16.090 --> 24:16.930
I wonder

24:17.420 --> 24:19.380
whether Si'en...

24:19.380 --> 24:20.250
You're courting death.

24:23.390 --> 24:24.290
Chief,

24:24.290 --> 24:25.730
You Guanyue is sowing discord.

24:26.290 --> 24:27.330
Don't fall for it.

24:30.090 --> 24:31.250
Was this arranged by you too?

24:32.290 --> 24:33.700
To attack the enemy,

24:34.810 --> 24:36.290
one must first attack the heart.

24:48.660 --> 24:49.500
Si'en,

24:50.490 --> 24:51.490
come to me.

24:51.770 --> 24:52.610
Chief,

24:53.490 --> 24:55.090
Si'en is your son.

24:55.090 --> 24:57.220
Chief, this is their scheme
to divide us.

25:11.770 --> 25:12.620
Chief.

25:12.660 --> 25:13.660
Take off your clothes.

25:14.490 --> 25:16.536
I've been loyal to the sect
and to you for decades.

25:16.940 --> 25:18.860
Can't that outweigh his few words?

25:21.530 --> 25:22.370
Chief.

25:22.980 --> 25:24.620
Will you take them off or not?

25:25.540 --> 25:26.380
Take them off.

25:26.380 --> 25:27.220
Chief.

25:56.140 --> 25:56.980
Chief!

25:57.490 --> 25:58.900
There must be deceit here.

26:09.570 --> 26:11.490
Why did you betray me?

26:11.490 --> 26:12.330
I didn't.

26:12.900 --> 26:14.980
You won't even acknowledge your son?

26:20.140 --> 26:20.980
Si'en,

26:21.810 --> 26:22.900
am I your father?

26:23.570 --> 26:24.420
Father,

26:24.420 --> 26:25.570
what's wrong?

26:26.090 --> 26:28.700
I'm your son, Father.

26:42.140 --> 26:42.980
No.

26:51.570 --> 26:52.730
I'll kill him to make amends.

26:52.730 --> 26:53.660
No!

26:54.006 --> 26:54.990
Since you won't admit it,

26:55.001 --> 26:56.330
I'll let him die before your eyes.

26:56.330 --> 26:57.530
Don't hurt him.

26:58.980 --> 27:01.010
He is your son.

27:01.620 --> 27:04.420
He is your son.

27:06.010 --> 27:06.850
Chief,

27:07.220 --> 27:08.700
this is their scheme to divide us.

27:08.980 --> 27:11.010
It's their scheme, Chief.

27:11.010 --> 27:11.850
Shut up.

27:18.620 --> 27:19.980
Since you refuse to believe me,

27:22.140 --> 27:24.220
I'll trade my life for his.

27:29.490 --> 27:31.700
Mother!

27:37.010 --> 27:38.090
Mother!

27:38.380 --> 27:40.700
My adoptive father
showed me great kindness.

27:41.660 --> 27:43.090
If not for him,

27:43.980 --> 27:45.900
how would I have married

27:46.490 --> 27:49.090
a foolish and petty man like you

27:49.940 --> 27:52.220
and suffered such humiliation?

27:53.250 --> 27:57.210
- I only pity my son.
- Mother!

27:57.860 --> 27:59.620
Mother!

28:02.290 --> 28:03.770
Mother!

28:03.770 --> 28:05.660
Don't leave me!

28:05.660 --> 28:06.570
Mother!

28:06.570 --> 28:09.380
Wake up! Look at me!

28:09.380 --> 28:11.660
Don't leave me!

28:11.660 --> 28:13.770
Today, I'll kill this brat!

28:13.770 --> 28:15.380
Mother!

28:19.490 --> 28:21.290
Mother!

28:22.570 --> 28:24.220
Ruxin didn't lie to you.

28:25.090 --> 28:26.980
That is your biological son.

28:26.980 --> 28:28.330
Why didn't you believe her?

28:28.330 --> 28:30.570
Why did you drive her to death?

28:30.570 --> 28:32.570
You'd even kill your own son.

28:32.570 --> 28:34.770
You've ruined the sect and ruined me.

28:35.620 --> 28:36.460
Stop!

28:47.380 --> 28:48.420
Who is the man in black?

28:49.050 --> 28:49.890
Who?

28:50.860 --> 28:53.180
I won't tell you.

28:54.090 --> 28:55.090
Once I die,

28:55.420 --> 28:57.660
the Six Sects will fall into chaos.

29:00.250 --> 29:02.730
Sooner or later,
you'll all be buried with me.

29:09.730 --> 29:10.570
Nie Zhe.

29:11.090 --> 29:11.930
Nie Zhe!

29:12.090 --> 29:13.090
Did I permit you to die?

29:13.770 --> 29:14.803
You're not allowed to die!

29:14.940 --> 29:16.220
You're not allowed to die!

29:16.220 --> 29:17.420
Father!

29:17.420 --> 29:19.050
You're not allowed to die!

29:19.050 --> 29:20.700
Mother!

29:23.490 --> 29:25.770
Father!

29:28.010 --> 29:30.180
Father!

29:35.620 --> 29:37.490
Father, Mother...

29:37.490 --> 29:38.330
Guanyue,

29:39.050 --> 29:40.140
issue the order at once.

29:40.140 --> 29:41.570
Gather the men from each altar

29:42.620 --> 29:43.980
and wipe out Nie Zhe's remnants.

29:44.180 --> 29:45.020
Yes.

29:47.010 --> 29:47.850
As for this child,

29:48.290 --> 29:49.620
find him a good family.

29:50.250 --> 29:51.090
Take him away.

29:51.090 --> 29:51.960
Father...

29:51.970 --> 29:52.820
Yes.

29:54.570 --> 29:56.490
I don't want to go with you.

29:57.380 --> 29:58.250
Father!

29:58.250 --> 29:59.530
Mother!

30:00.290 --> 30:01.180
Father!

30:01.180 --> 30:02.570
Mother!

30:03.290 --> 30:05.700
Mother!

30:06.900 --> 30:10.220
Father!

30:16.530 --> 30:17.420
All of this

30:19.290 --> 30:20.900
was part of your plan.

30:21.620 --> 30:23.050
I intended to use Yu Huiyin

30:24.010 --> 30:25.140
to capture Nie Zhe alive

30:26.770 --> 30:28.416
and learn
the man in black's whereabouts.

30:30.290 --> 30:31.530
So, it means

30:33.220 --> 30:34.530
that except for Nie Zhe's death,

30:35.420 --> 30:36.940
everything went as you wished.

30:37.420 --> 30:38.700
Suspicion is like wildfire.

30:39.180 --> 30:40.490
A single spark can start a blaze.

30:41.940 --> 30:43.940
Nie Zhe was always deeply suspicious.

30:45.700 --> 30:47.010
Impressive tactics indeed.

30:47.490 --> 30:49.180
Whether Yu Huiyin lived or died,

30:49.570 --> 30:50.590
he'd surely grow estranged

30:51.570 --> 30:52.900
from Nie Zhe after this scheme.

30:54.010 --> 30:55.620
But why use Nie Zhe

30:55.620 --> 30:56.480
to kill Li Ruxin?

30:56.480 --> 30:57.660
I never meant for her to die.

31:05.620 --> 31:06.460
Zhao,

31:08.730 --> 31:09.770
you still don't believe me.

31:12.700 --> 31:14.140
I don't believe you didn't foresee

31:14.140 --> 31:15.490
this outcome.

31:16.770 --> 31:17.610
Why?

31:18.860 --> 31:20.290
Why do this?

31:21.420 --> 31:22.570
Only by doing this

31:23.330 --> 31:24.770
can black and white be separated,

31:25.363 --> 31:27.083
and loyalty and treachery
be distinguished.

31:27.730 --> 31:28.700
Only by doing this

31:28.946 --> 31:30.619
can Bliss Palace
and the Hanhai Mountains,

31:30.630 --> 31:31.910
you and I,

31:32.250 --> 31:33.660
find true peace.

31:42.530 --> 31:43.900
Now, everything is over.

31:44.700 --> 31:45.540
Stay,

31:46.570 --> 31:47.410
okay?

31:49.940 --> 31:50.900
I don't understand.

31:57.050 --> 31:59.050
Did you really have to go this far?

32:45.420 --> 32:50.900
(Carefree)

33:05.290 --> 33:06.130
Zhao.

33:09.860 --> 33:10.700
Zhao.

33:40.220 --> 33:41.060
Zhao.

34:05.810 --> 34:07.050
I thought you left.

34:10.740 --> 34:11.780
It's good you didn't.

34:20.980 --> 34:22.010
The poison in you

34:22.340 --> 34:23.273
must be cleared slowly.

34:24.490 --> 34:26.010
Don't recklessly use your qi again.

34:27.050 --> 34:29.130
I planted some blood-activating herbs.

34:29.940 --> 34:30.990
They'll help you

34:31.001 --> 34:32.221
dispel the poison and recover.

34:32.900 --> 34:34.860
When you have time, brew them in water.

34:35.470 --> 34:36.970
Add some goji berries and brown sugar.

34:37.170 --> 34:38.010
It tastes good.

34:42.610 --> 34:43.450
Zhao,

34:43.690 --> 34:44.610
I'll release

34:45.210 --> 34:46.316
all the Six Sects' families.

34:46.740 --> 34:47.690
Except for Nie Zhe,

34:47.690 --> 34:49.063
I'll give everyone a proper burial.

34:49.780 --> 34:50.980
Once the purge is finished,

34:51.610 --> 34:53.130
I'll order the Youming Path sealed.

34:54.050 --> 34:55.130
We'll stay here forever

34:56.210 --> 34:57.170
and never part again,

34:58.260 --> 34:59.100
okay?

35:03.420 --> 35:04.260
Oh, right.

35:05.570 --> 35:06.820
Uncle Cheng just said

35:07.170 --> 35:08.490
Xue Youfu needs me.

35:09.820 --> 35:10.860
I'll go over first.

35:39.860 --> 35:40.900
Fire starter.

35:46.130 --> 35:46.970
Bamboo hat.

35:49.610 --> 35:50.690
Straw raincoat.

35:51.860 --> 35:53.170
You don't know.

35:53.170 --> 35:55.260
Every altar is clearing out
the Nie remnants.

35:55.260 --> 35:56.530
It's chaotic.

35:56.530 --> 35:57.745
Those tied to Nie Zhe

35:57.756 --> 35:58.980
are fleeing one after another.

35:58.980 --> 36:00.490
These items are selling fast.

36:00.490 --> 36:01.490
Miss Cai,

36:01.490 --> 36:02.570
I saved a set just for you.

36:04.980 --> 36:05.860
Thank you, Uncle Xue.

36:07.340 --> 36:09.900
The Young Master just let them leave?

36:10.130 --> 36:11.490
I heard from Master You

36:11.980 --> 36:14.340
that he won't make things hard
for those who want to go.

36:14.340 --> 36:16.079
As long as they leave
the Hanhai Mountains,

36:16.090 --> 36:17.340
he won't pursue them.

36:18.210 --> 36:19.170
I also heard

36:20.610 --> 36:22.690
he plans to seal the Youming Path

36:22.690 --> 36:24.490
and cut off contact
with the outside world.

36:24.490 --> 36:25.330
Miss Cai,

36:25.740 --> 36:26.580
is that true?

36:31.740 --> 36:32.940
I'm not sure.

36:33.490 --> 36:34.490
Uncle Xue,

36:34.490 --> 36:36.070
if there's nothing else, I'll be going.

36:37.530 --> 36:38.420
Miss Cai,

36:39.900 --> 36:41.260
may I ask you something?

36:50.820 --> 36:52.300
The Pingshu

36:53.210 --> 36:54.610
Zhengyang spoke of...

36:54.610 --> 36:56.210
Was she your aunt,

36:56.860 --> 36:57.820
Cai Pingshu?

36:59.300 --> 37:00.300
You guessed.

37:00.610 --> 37:02.210
I wasn't certain before.

37:02.570 --> 37:04.260
But when I was packing to flee,

37:04.740 --> 37:06.580
I found a painting
Zhengyang made while drunk.

37:07.090 --> 37:08.490
The woman in it

37:08.490 --> 37:09.490
has a bearing like yours.

37:13.900 --> 37:14.820
It was my aunt.

37:15.900 --> 37:17.530
So, it truly was Cai Pingshu.

37:17.530 --> 37:18.370
No wonder.

37:18.940 --> 37:20.380
Zhengyang said Pingshu

37:20.380 --> 37:21.690
was an extraordinary woman.

37:26.010 --> 37:26.900
Uncle Xue,

37:28.610 --> 37:29.940
what kind of person

37:30.820 --> 37:32.340
was Mu Zhengyang?

37:35.001 --> 37:45.661
=Generation to Generation=

38:04.421 --> 38:08.831
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

38:09.396 --> 38:14.011
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

38:14.351 --> 38:18.916
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

38:19.441 --> 38:23.741
♪Free to wander in the world♪

38:26.686 --> 38:31.386
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:31.911 --> 38:36.201
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:36.861 --> 38:40.891
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:41.206 --> 38:46.331
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:46.906 --> 38:51.716
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:51.931 --> 38:56.101
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:56.826 --> 39:00.761
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:01.261 --> 39:06.536
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

39:29.266 --> 39:34.396
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:34.761 --> 39:39.131
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:39.396 --> 39:43.526
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:43.711 --> 39:49.286
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
